_header: All that loveth gods lore / Old and young less and more
Subjects: Eustace, saints, life of; saints’ lives
_description: Life of St Eustace — in seventy-one 6-line stanzas

BodAsh61.Note:
Lines 1-30 only; on torn leaf affixed to flyleaf, together with part of
                    the list of contents of this MS.

BodDig86.First Lines:
Alle þat louieþ Godes loreOlde and ȝonge lasse and
                    more…
BodDig86.Last Lines:
…Wiþ ihesu seinte marie soneEuere wiþ houten
                    hende
